<plot>Everybody dies... every single one of us. In an instant, life and perception end, years of memories vanish. Will you recognize that moment? Or, will you carry on, seamlessly transitioning to a new reality? Vincent has transitioned, but he is unaware of his new place in this world. As he travels deeper into the afterlife his fate becomes painfully clear... there is no escape.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?185345</url></doc>
